Author: foxescanflyvu
Text: Ughhh same!! I used to basically only eat fruit (cause fruit calories don't matter right?!?) and now I can't eat one (1) apple without peanut butter. Likewise with quinoa, frozen berries (my old solution to hunger), celery,  and honestly I even have trouble drinking enough water because it reminds me of inhaling like 3 gallons of fluid everyday to keep my appetite at bay.
